'''哈桑·本·阿里·图尔克马尼[[中将|中将]]'''（{{lang-ar|'''العماد حسن بن علي توركماني'''}}）{{BD|1935年|1月1日|2012年|7月18日|catIdx=Rajiha, Dawoud}}是已故[[叙利亚|叙利亚]][[政治人物|政治人物]]、[[叙利亚军事|叙利亚陆军]][[军官|军官]]，曾任叙陆军参谋长、国防部长、武装部队副总司令<ref name=Bar_S.436>{{cite journal|last=Bar|first=Shmuel|title=Bashar's Syria: The Regime and its Strategic Worldview|journal=Comparative Strategy|year=2006|volume=25|pages=436|url=http://www.herzliyaconference.org/_Uploads/2590Bashars.pdf|accessdate=15 May 2011|archive-date=2011-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723214138/http://www.herzliyaconference.org/_Uploads/2590Bashars.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，已在[[2012年7月大马士革炸弹袭击事件|一起爆炸事件]]中遇难。<ref name=reu1812>{{cite news|title=Bomb kills men at heart of Assad rule as Syria fight rages|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/18/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE8610SH20120718|accessdate=18 July 2012|newspaper=Reuters|date=18 July 2012|author=Dominic Evans|author2=Khaled Yacoub Oweis|archive-date=2012-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120906011524/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/18/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE8610SH20120718|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==早年生活和教育==
图尔克马尼于1935年出生在[[阿勒颇|阿勒颇]]的一个[[土耳其族|土耳其族]][[逊尼派|逊尼派]][[穆斯林|穆斯林]]家庭。<ref name=cri>[http://gb.cri.cn/3821/2004/05/13/622@157479.htm  叙利亚总统巴沙尔任命图尔克马尼为新国防部长]</ref><ref name=meib/>他于1954年从[[军校|军校]][[炮兵|炮兵]][[专业|专业]][[毕业|毕业]]，获[[陆军|陆军]][[中尉|中尉]][[军衔|军衔]]<ref name=meib/>并加入[[叙利亚军事|叙利亚陆军]]。

==职业生涯==
图尔克马尼曾指挥一个机械化[[师_(军队)|师]]参加了1973年[[第三次中东战争|第三次中东战争]]<ref name=cri/>。1978年他晋升[[少将|少将]]。<ref name=meib/>他于2002年1月接替[[阿里·阿斯兰|阿里·阿斯兰]]中将，成为叙陆军参谋长。<ref name=meib>{{cite journal|last=Gambill|first=Gary C.|title=The Military-Intelligence Shakeup in Syria|journal=Middle East Intelligence Bulletin|date=February 2002|volume=4|issue=2|url=http://www.meforum.org/meib/articles/0202_s1.htm|accessdate=7 July 2012|archive-date=2019-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507121032/https://www.meforum.org/meib/articles/0202_s1.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>因为他是一名逊尼派穆斯林，他的任命被认为是恢复了叙利亚军事和情报部门宗教多样性的举动，而之前很长一段时期这些部门是由[[什叶派|什叶派]][[阿拉维派|阿拉维派]]把持的。<ref name=meib/>  

2004年5月12日，[[巴沙尔·阿萨德|巴沙尔·阿萨德]][[叙利亚总统|总统]]颁布命令，任命图尔克马尼为新任国防部长兼武装部队副总司令，接替当天[[退休|退休]]的[[穆斯塔法·塔拉斯|穆斯塔法·塔拉斯]]。<ref name=cri/>他于2009年6月3日卸任，接替他的是原叙陆军参谋长[[阿里·哈比卜·马哈茂德|阿里·哈比卜·马哈茂德]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=Syria names new defence minister|author=|newspaper=[[France_24|France 24]]|date=3 June 2009|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20090603-syria-names-new-defence-minister}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>同日，巴沙尔总统任命他为部长级别的副总统助理。<ref name=globalsec>{{cite web|title=Syria Military. Defense Ministry|url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/syria/defense.htm|publisher=Global Security|accessdate=5 July 2012|archive-date=2018-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181211220611/https://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/syria/defense.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>他还被任命为政府危机处理部门负责人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tibet.cn/news/gjxw/201207/t20120719_1761229.htm |title=叙利亚国家安全总部遭袭击 国防部长等多名高官伤亡 |accessdate=2012-07-22 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114911/http://www.tibet.cn/news/gjxw/201207/t20120719_1761229.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并被指应对叙利亚的滥用[[酷刑|酷刑]]状况负责。<ref name=tdbeast>{{cite news|last=Ibish|first=Hussein|title=Assad is Doomed|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2012/07/18/assad-is-doomed.html|accessdate=17 July 2012|newspaper=The Daily Beast|date=17 July 2012|archive-date=2012-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120722035145/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2012/07/18/assad-is-doomed.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他也是叙副总统[[法鲁克·沙雷|法鲁克·沙雷]]的军事[[顾问|顾问]]。<ref name=nyt1812>{{cite news|title=Blast Kills Core Syrian Security Officials|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/19/world/middleeast/suicide-attack-reported-in-damascus-as-more-generals-flee.html?pagewanted=all|accessdate=18 July 2012|newspaper=The New York Times|date=18 July 2012|author=Neil MacFarquhar|author2=Dalal Mawad|archive-date=2012-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120721201459/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/19/world/middleeast/suicide-attack-reported-in-damascus-as-more-generals-flee.html?pagewanted=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==传闻死亡==
2012年5月20日，反政府组织[[叙利亚自由军|叙利亚自由军]]的大马士革委员会宣称，该组织的一个[[营|营]]已经成功逮捕了政府危机处理机构、即负责叙政府军日常事务的所有八名成员。自由军还称，他们相信这八人中至少有六人——前国防部长图尔克马尼、现国防部长[[达乌德·拉吉哈|拉吉哈]]、现国防部副部长[[阿塞夫·肖卡特|肖卡特]]、现内政部长[[穆罕默德·易卜拉欣·沙尔|沙尔]]、现国家安全顾问[[希沙姆·伊赫蒂亚尔|伊赫蒂亚尔]]和[[复兴党|复兴党]]（叙利亚）地区领导机构副总书记[[穆罕默德·赛义德·布希坦|布-{希}-坦]]——已经被杀死。不过很快内政部长沙尔和图尔克马尼先后在国家电视台露面粉碎谣言，并称谣言是“彻头彻尾毫无根据”的。<ref name=tgmay>{{cite news|title=Six senior figures in Assad regime killed, rebel army says|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2012/may/20/syria-damascus-clashes-assassinations#block-12|accessdate=19 July 2012|newspaper=The Guardian|date=May 2012|archive-date=2012-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120723223620/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2012/may/20/syria-damascus-clashes-assassinations#block-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=aarabiya20may>{{cite news|title=High-ranking Syrian officials deny reports of their own assassinations|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/05/20/215270.html|accessdate=19 July 2012|newspaper=Al Arabiya|date=20 May 2012|archive-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010045412/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/05/20/215270.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==身亡==
{{main|2012年7月大马士革炸弹袭击事件}}

在传闻被暗杀近两个月后，图尔克马尼于2012年7月18日在位于大马士革西北部[[花园广场|花园广场]]的叙利亚国家安全总部大楼发生的[[自杀式袭击|自杀式袭击]]中被[[爆炸|炸]]身亡，当时高官们正在举行会议，同时死亡的还有时任国防部长[[达乌德·拉吉哈|达乌德·拉吉哈]]中将和巴沙尔总统的姐夫、国防部副部长[[阿塞夫·肖卡特|阿塞夫·肖卡特]]中将<ref>{{cite web|title=Syria defence minister killed in Damascus bomb|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9408303/Syria-defence-minister-killed-in-Damascus-bomb.html|publisher=The Telegraph|accessdate=18 July 2012|archive-date=2012-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120721074457/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9408303/Syria-defence-minister-killed-in-Damascus-bomb.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Syria conflict: 'Suicide bomb' kills defence minister|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18882149|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=18 July 2012|archive-date=2012-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120722123320/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18882149|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=bbc1812>{{cite news|title=Syria ministers 'killed in blast'|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18889030|accessdate=18 July 2012|newspaper=BBC|date=18 July 2012|archive-date=2012-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120720233355/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18889030|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其他许多高官（包括被传身亡后证实还活着的内政部长[[穆罕默德·易卜拉欣·沙尔|穆罕默德·易卜拉欣·沙尔]]）则受伤<ref>{{cite web |url=http://int.gmw.cn/2012-07/18/content_4583251.htm |language= |title=叙利亚国家安全总部遭袭 国防部长被炸死 |publisher=新华网 |date=2012-07-18 |accessdate= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120721084459/http://int.gmw.cn/2012-07/18/content_4583251.htm |archivedate=2012-07-21 }}</ref>。7月20日在大马士革举行了图尔克马尼、拉吉哈和肖卡特三人的[[国葬|国葬]]。<ref name=naharnet2012>{{cite news|title=Syria National Security Chief Dies of Wounds, State Funerals Held for Slain Officials|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/47225-syria-national-security-chief-dies-of-wounds-state-funerals-held-for-slain-officials|accessdate=21 July 2012|newspaper=Naharnet|date=20 July 2012|archive-date=2012-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120722020330/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/47225-syria-national-security-chief-dies-of-wounds-state-funerals-held-for-slain-officials|dead-url=no}}</ref>

